{"tid":2328953,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯仍是老大！年度分析他力壓利雲度夫斯基","createTime":"2020-12-17T01:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T02:50:00.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f762d90dad4b316720e3f399652c78606d3ec01c","tid":2328953,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"　　根據《Carteret》的數據分析系統，2020年表現最好的球員是美斯（Lionel Messi），而C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）進不了前十名。<br />\n<br />\n　　該系統分析每名球員對自己球隊贏波所起的作用，並以此得出「Carteret評分」。美斯的綜合評分達到317.4分，為所有球員之首。<br />\n<br />\n　　排在第二的是拜仁慕尼黑中鋒利雲度夫斯基，得分310.3分，曼城的迪布尼（Kevin De Bruyne）（297.9）和熱刺的哈利-簡尼（Harry Kane）（274.9）分列第三和第四名。<br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度的評分為235.5分，未能進入前十名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PP9s4dx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPP9s4dx.jpg&h=8a5d089c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a5a946f5b78b04c0e2c151496214edd408e3499","tid":2328953,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"箂萬多夫斯基<br />\n<br />\n利咩雲"},{"pid":"5af1a4a6ea57ede43c86cf6c5ee3eaf64130d135","tid":2328953,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T02:50:00.000Z","msg":"評分準則係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得一個後衛，一個龍都冇"}]}